Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoardMaker
    this class offers static methods to the panels of the GUI to draw the Boardproxy on the window of the application.
    BoardPanel
    this class represents the actual game board that the user interacts with.
    ChooseGodsPanel
    The panel in charge of the "choosing god" phase of the game
    GetImages
    this class loads the Images to display heroes and tower's stories on the board in a way that is compatible with JAR packaging.
    GUILoader  
    LoginPanel
    first panel to be displayed when the application boots up, must have all login and connection configure options
    StaticFrame
    this class is in charge of the management of the main frame of the application.
